Central Atlas Tamazight (nke a na-akpọkwa Tamazight) bụ nke ngalaba Northern Berber nke asụsụ Berber.[nb 1]
Dị ka onye otu ezinụlọ Afroasiatic, ụtọ asụsụ Tamazight nwere usoro nwoke na nwanyị abụọ (tawsit), ụdị VSO, ụdaume siri ike (nke emere na Tamazight dị ka velarized), na ọdịdị templatic.
